Version:	2.5.5
Release:	1
License:	(FTL or GPLv2+) and BSD and MIT and Public Domain and zlib with acknowledgement
URL:		http://www.freetype.org/
Group:		System Environment/Libraries
Vendor:		VMware, Inc.
